OL,3,CRapist surgeon pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmisusing patient records
OL,6,FA trainee surgeon who was jailed for
OL,7,Fraping women in Devon and Cornwall has
OL,8,Fnow pleaded guilty to misusing patient
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,FSalil Korambayil, from Redhill in
OL,12,FSurrey, attacked and raped the two
OL,13,Fvictims in their own homes after
OL,14,Fmeeting them on social media.
OL,16,FHe was convicted by a jury after
OL,17,Fdenying three counts of rape, at Truro
OL,18,FCrown Court in November 2023.
OL,20,FThe 32-year-old was jailed for 14
OL,21,Fyears.
