OL,3,CRapist surgeon pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmisusing patient records
OL,6,FNow Korambayil has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fthree charges relating to misuse of
OL,8,Frecords at hospital trusts in Devon
OL,9,Fand Cornwall.
OL,11,FHe was sentenced to 12 months for this
OL,12,Fon Thursday 29 August, to be served
OL,13,Fconsecutively with the sentence for
OL,14,Frape.
OL,16,FFurther information on the rape
OL,17,Foffences have now been released since
OL,18,Fsentencing has concluded for the data
OL,19,Fbreach case.
