OL,3,CRapist surgeon pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmisusing patient records
OL,6,FOne of the rape offences took place in
OL,7,FNorth Devon in August 2020 and the
OL,8,Fother two happened in Cornwall in
OL,9,FMarch 2021.
OL,11,FKorambayil had worked in hospitals as
OL,12,Fa trainee colorectal and vascular
OL,13,Fsurgeon between 2016 and 2021.
