OL,3,CRapist surgeon pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cmisusing patient records
OL,6,FSentencing Korambayil for the rapes in
OL,7,FDecember 2023, Judge Simon Carr told
OL,8,Fhim: "You deliberately targeted women
OL,9,Fwho were very much older than you. You
OL,10,Ffound them on the internet. You saw
OL,11,Fpictures of them. You were very aware
OL,12,Fof the age gap. In the case of both of
OL,13,Fthem, you spent over a year grooming
OL,14,Fthem - there's no other word."
OL,16,FPersonal statements from both victims
OL,17,Fwere read out in court.
