OL,6,FOne said that, since the rape, she has
OL,7,Flost confidence and no longer feels
OL,8,Fcomfortable walking alone. If she must
OL,9,Fgo somewhere on her own, she travels
OL,10,Fby car, even for short journeys. She
OL,11,Fexperiences panic attacks and takes
OL,12,Fmedication to control these.
OL,14,FShe suffers from loss of sleep, has
OL,15,Fexperienced a decline in her mental
OL,16,Fhealth and endures rapid mood swings.
