OL,6,FShe said: "I have a constant nightmare
OL,7,Fof being chased and hunted down, I
OL,8,Falso sometimes wake myself up
OL,9,Fscreaming. In the morning, I don't
OL,10,Ffeel as though I have slept at all,
OL,11,Fand I constantly wake up during the
OL,12,Fnight."
OL,14,FThe second victim described how, prior
OL,15,Fto the attack, she had been resilient,
OL,16,Fprofessional and vivacious, with a
OL,17,Fwide circle of friends. Since that day
OL,18,Fshe is haunted by flashbacks and
OL,19,Fnightmares and felt 'broken' by the
OL,20,Fexperience.
