OL,6,FShe said that everything she does now
OL,7,Fis in solitude. She has lost faith in
OL,8,Fthe medical and surgical profession,
OL,9,Fand suffers panic attacks during
OL,10,Fexaminations.
OL,12,FThe victim added: "Despite all the
OL,13,Fdisruption, distress and trauma, you
OL,14,Fdid one thing right in all of this and
OL,15,Fthat was to underestimate me. I take
OL,16,Fcomfort and pride in knowing that your
OL,17,Fdecision to pick on me that night, led
OL,18,Fto you eventually paying for your
OL,19,Fcrimes."
