OL,4,Cmisusing patient records
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Daniel Massey, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation, under the name
OL,8,FOperation Humulis, said: "I would want
OL,9,Fto highlight to everyone that this
OL,10,Foutcome is more about the courageous
OL,11,Fvictims, who were so brave to not only
OL,12,Fcome forward and report what had
OL,13,Fhappened to them, but to also remain
OL,14,Fengaged throughout the process.
OL,16,F"It is also about justice for these
OL,17,Fvictims and their loved ones, as being
OL,18,Fable to see Salil Korambayil convicted
OL,19,Ffor these truly awful crimes is a
OL,20,Fpositive for all.
